<i>noun</i>: 호화 [호화], 호사 [호사] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>호화 [호화]</dt><br>
<dd>luxury; sumptuousness; flashiness</dd><br>
<dd>사치스럽고 화려함.</dd><br>
<dd>A state of being luxurious and fancy.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>호사 [호사]</dt><br>
<dd>luxury; extravagance</dd><br>
<dd>화려하고 사치스럽게 지냄.</dd><br>
<dd>A state of living a luxurious and fancy life.</dd><br>
</li>
